#SAS2021 was off the chain!! 🌴🔥

Huge shout out to @charliekirk1776 and @turningpointusa for putting on an amazing event, and giving me the opportunity to speak! 

It was such a blessing to meet you all in Tampa! 

Click the link in the bio to watch my full speech at the event on YouTube! 

IN THE END WE WIN! 👏🏽

🎶-S/O to @iamlozaalexander9 for the song 🔥

#SAS2021 was off the chain!! 🌴🔥

Huge shout out to @charliekirk1776 and @turningpointusa for putting on an amazing event, and giving me the opportunity to speak! 

It was such a blessing to meet you all in Tampa! 

Click the link in the bio to watch my full speech at the event on YouTube! 

IN THE END WE WIN! 👏🏽

🎶-S/O to @iamlozaalexander9 for the song 🔥
